{"tid":2491212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳奕迅IG刪剩3個post 做護棉手捲政治風波疑暗示想「唱歌好好拍電影」？","createTime":"2021-04-16T06:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T07:17:44.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"26ac3770eaf4b167b1f1a0203fce76782d7466ac","tid":2491212,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:50:19.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅(Eason)早前宣布與合作逾十年的adidas割席，事件引來勁大迴響，之後婉拒無綫及ViuTV的演出似避風頭。近日Eason刪走多則IG帖文，只剩下3則帖文，分別是曾比特(Mike)的歌曲《我不如》、一支錄音咪及文念中執導的電影《好好拍電影》海報。由於過去Eason有刪po的習慣，有網民認為他留下這3則帖文似是表達自己只會專心唱歌及演好角色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/4/1618518161_JL-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F4%2F1618518161_JL-1280w.jpg&h=49fee77c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"922f63fa2bf835b74eced09ad5c76ecceb53f662","tid":2491212,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:01:14.000Z","msg":"暗你娘<br />\n唔愛共就中共地區收皮，<br />\n愛共就中共外地區收皮。"},{"pid":"5f7e6b957451ecafdae7a695fc0c74fd35b55dcd","tid":2491212,"uid":210669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks"},{"pid":"bfd62212ca21c5de1e9aaaa1bdd339b326469072","tid":2491212,"uid":76804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:04:10.000Z","msg":"香港呢d所謂藝人真係乞衣<br />\n以為咩都唔關自己事<br />\n唔好煩我 <br />\n淨係想賺錢 淨係想唱歌做戲<br />\n含撚啦好心<br />\n<br />\n做公眾人物 <br />\n荷里活班左膠都識得用個人影響力發聲<br />\n香港呢班除左奶共就乜撚都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa04c5a83087ffccd1102e4074f5ea0026a73596","tid":2491212,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:07:40.000Z","msg":"Still no thanks"},{"pid":"1c87cb53a7f1a985c9c367599303bfc6d6516451","tid":2491212,"uid":305638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:08:29.000Z",